# AI-Powered Knowledge Assistant Platform 🤖

A full-stack GenAI web app blending **Software Development** and **LLM technology**.

## 🚀 Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** React + TailwindCSS
- **Backend:** FastAPI / Node.js (Express)
- **Database:** MongoDB / PostgreSQL
- **LLM Integration:** OpenAI API / Hugging Face Transformers
- **Deployment:** Vercel + Render

## ✨ Features
- Secure user authentication (JWT)
- File upload (PDF/Text)
- Contextual Q&A using LLMs
- Vector database with FAISS/Chroma
- Admin dashboard & usage analytics

## 🧠 How It Works
1. User uploads documents or enters queries.
2. Backend stores and embeds the data using SentenceTransformers.
3. Relevant context is retrieved for each query.
4. LLM (GPT/HuggingFace) generates human-like responses.
5. Frontend displays results in a real-time chat interface.

## 🔍 Skills Demonstrated
- Backend API development  
- Frontend integration with React  
- Database design  
- Large Language Model (LLM) integration  
- Cloud deployment & security

## 📦 Setup
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ai-knowledge-assistant.git
cd ai-knowledge-assistant
